'''約翰·威克斯'''（{{lang-en|John Weeks}}，{{bd|1941年||2020年|7月26日|catIdx=Weeks}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://countercurrents.org/2020/07/prof-john-weeks-humanised-economics-as-a-discipline/|title=Prof John Weeks Humanised Economics as a Discipline|last1=Shankar Nayak|first1=Bhabani|date=2020-07-27|website=Counter Currents|access-date=2020-07-27|archive-date=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728044341/https://countercurrents.org/2020/07/prof-john-weeks-humanised-economics-as-a-discipline/|dead-url=no}}</ref>），美国[[經濟學家|經濟學家]]，[[倫敦大學亞非學院|倫敦大學亞非學院]]經濟學系榮譽教授。研究興趣包含[[總體經濟學|總體經濟學]]與[[發展經濟學|發展經濟學]]理論與政策應用。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.soas.ac.uk/staff/staff60157.php|title=SOAS staff listing|access-date=2010-09-14|archive-date=2019-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191201145302/https://www.soas.ac.uk/staff/staff60157.php|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://jweeks.org/ |title=Weeks' personal home page |accessdate=2020-09-16 |archive-date=2019-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191121073714/http://jweeks.org/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 他以提出“量化競爭理論”來反映市場中越多競爭（生產者、消費者和工人），經濟就越有效率的前提而聞名。<ref name="FineSaad-Filho2012">{{cite book|last1=Fine|first1=Ben|last2=Saad-Filho|first2=Alfredo|last3=Boffo|first3=Marco|title=The Elgar Companion to Marxist Economics|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=xe0VQArHt8sC&pg=PR12|accessdate=2013-11-23|date=2012-01-01|publisher=Edward Elgar Publishing|isbn=9781781001226|pages=12|archive-date=2014-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103091913/http://books.google.com/books?id=xe0VQArHt8sC&pg=PR12|dead-url=no}}</ref>

